  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Making Climate Finance Transformational</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">This special project focused on international climate finance architecture and support for the establishment of the Green Climate Fund (GCF). The topics covered included research on access for emerging and developing countries to international climate finance and in particular to the GCF, on mobilising the private sector for investment in climate protection, and on the transformative impact of climate finance. In the framework of this programme, WRI also conducted workshops on capacity building and transparency for representatives of developing countries and NGOs.</narrative>
  </description>
